      "review_summary": "Adds an optional heartbeat `transcriptMode` config, threads it into embedded-runner context filtering, documents the modes, and adds heartbeat-filter regression coverage for `strip-all`, `keep-result`, and `keep-all`.\n\nPR surface: Source +155, Tests +368, Docs +13. Total +536 across 9 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. for the review findings by source inspection: the schema accepts `transcriptMode` while the config-honor inventory omits it, and the docs' failed-ack retention note conflicts with the PR's pending/failed response-tool tests. I did not run tests because this review is read-only.",
